{"type": "article", "id": 17814, "title": "这所打开了一半的房子，向天空多要一些阳光", "description": "实用主义者一定会说：这得多容易落灰啊！", "date": "2015-11-19T16:10:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14006, "name": "住宅设计"}, {"id": 19007, "name": "SYAP"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 162, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702122401upgieKDzC193qcas.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t坐落于日本三重县四日市的这所方形建筑一定会让所有路过的人停下来。它的屋顶没有完全合起来，让光线毫无顾忌地放射出去，屋子周围也没有栅栏，像一个打开了一半的潘多拉魔盒。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t来自东京的建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://syap.jp/news_/\" target=\"_blank\">SYAP</a> 设计了这个住宅，倾斜的屋顶和墙面之间的开口其实是用玻璃封起来了。因为坐北朝南，能让光线最大化照射到屋子深处。到了晚上，屋子里明亮的光线会透到外面去，非常醒目。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t屋顶的开口角度经过细心的调整，正好可以看到远处的山脉。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122353D9nZuVroaRcpj0zC.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122353HbvsfiI1jWSdwYOQ.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t住宅有上下两层，楼上的卧室两侧悬空，像是单独挂在屋子里的。靠近屋顶开口处的两侧墙都用玻璃镶嵌，使光线能从上面传递到一楼。一楼朝南的墙面也用了大窗户，让整体空间都透明开放。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t室内统一使用浅色的木材，墙面保留自然的木纹，让光线的反射变得柔和。卧室、餐厅、厨房都是半开放的，以营造更加密切的居家气氛。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122354rqEN0AmcK329oi8s.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021223546zckF3sfoatAJKuQ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1120\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.36919315\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122355b9a75wILdD2A1ivY.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1403\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">悬挂的二楼卧室\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122355zEYWN0cMrxBiFPa8.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1403\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">二楼的玻璃墙面\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122356AbXL6alu5jOJkKBo.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\"二楼走廊\" alt=\"二楼走廊\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>二楼走廊</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122356EFqOg4hy2BKu7C8X.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\"从二楼看一楼\" alt=\"从二楼看一楼\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>从二楼看一楼</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122359SYnLO9J6IydeT2Dc.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1072\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.31051345\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122359uHoWr2CMZF5A6XOT.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"974\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"1.19070905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122400jpBTSDYz6XC3FhUk.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\"一楼\" alt=\"一楼\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>一楼</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t与周围其他住宅不同的是，它没有围上栅栏，地面铺上与周围环境协调的石子，以更加适应社区的环境。设计者想让这个开放的空间真正融入到社区中去。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122400l3A1QModPt2bxpBY.gif\" width=\"460\" height=\"202\" title=\"平面图\" alt=\"平面图\" data-ratio=\"0.43913043\" data-format=\"gif\"><span>平面图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片来自\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/11/18/house-yokkaichi-syap-lantern-open-box-roof-japan/\" target=\"_blank\">dezeen</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}